## Anti-Patterns (Avoid)

❌ Too many colors - stick to color system
❌ Heavy shadows - use subtle shadows only
❌ Crowded layouts - generous spacing always
❌ Too many font weights - max 3 weights
❌ Complex gradients - solid colors preferred
❌ Busy backgrounds - clean, simple
❌ Information overload - progressive disclosure
❌ Too many borders - use sparingly

